title: AmLactin 12 % Moisturizing Lotion - 567 g / 20 oz
description: The active ingredient is 12% lactic acid neutralized with ammonium hydroxide. This natural AHA is equivalent to other prescription lactic acid moisturizing agents. Great for seriously dry skin conditions like eczema, icthyoses, psoriasis and keratosis pilaris. In a lighter base for those with oilier skin types, or those who live in humid climates.
